text: José Roberto Reynoso Fernandez (born 7 July 1947) is a Brazilian equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:Brazilian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Brazil Category:Equestrians at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Pan American Games medalists in equestrian Category:Pan American Games gold medalists for Brazil Category:Equestrians at the 1967 Pan American Games Category:Sportspeople from São Paulo
title: José Fernandez (equestrian)
